	<h1 class="title">从《花样年华》到《聂隐娘》，是这些人决定了你看到它们是什么样子|电影时尚</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Grace</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-21 08:38:24 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17885/medium/17885.jpg?1448060061" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


